sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_044_3_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Firmware Update - Installation Failed
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Firmware Management feature profile

    CS->>CP: 1. UpdateFirmware.req
    Note right of CS: location: <Firmware Download URL><br/>(NOTE: field not in CSMS spec, inferred)
    CP-->>CS: 2. UpdateFirmware.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point starts downloading firmware

    CP->>CS: 3. FirmwareStatusNotification.req (status: Downloading)
    CS-->>CP: 4. FirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point finishes downloading firmware

    CP->>CS: 5. FirmwareStatusNotification.req (status: Downloaded)
    CS-->>CP: 6. FirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point reports connector status

    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req (status: Unavailable)
    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point starts installing firmware

    CP->>CS: 9. FirmwareStatusNotification.req (status: Installing)
    CS-->>CP: 10. FirmwareStatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point reboots

    CP->>CS: 11. BootNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 12. BootNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Charge Point reports connector status

    CP->>CS: 13. StatusNotification.req (status: Available)
    CS-->>CP: 14. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: Installation has failed

    CP->>CS: 15. FirmwareStatusNotification.req (status: InstallationFailed)
    CS-->>CP: 16. FirmwareStatusNotification.conf
